title: The Nets are Done, and the Grizzlies and T-Wolves Are Tied 2-2 | Weekends with Wos
description:
Wos is joined by Bleacher Report and The Athletic’s Mo Dakhil to discuss the Celtics' dismantling of the Nets. They also look ahead to the Nets' offseason, and wonder how far the Celtics can go in the playoffs (2:40). Then, they discuss the Timberwolves tying their series against the Grizzlies (24:46).

Host: Wosny Lambre
Guest: Mo Dakhil
Associate Producer: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Benjamin Cruz
